<lb n="0491b03" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0491009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本</note>佛說呪齒經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0491b04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0491b05" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">東晉<note n="0491010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（西域三藏）＋竺【三】</note><note n="0491010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">竺【大】，西域三藏竺【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0491010"><lem wit="【大】">竺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">西域三藏竺</rdg></app>曇無蘭譯</byline>
<lb n="0491b06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0491b0601">南無佛南無法南無比丘僧南無舍利弗大目
<lb n="0491b07" ed="T"/><note n="0491011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">乾＝揵【三】</note><note n="0491011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乾【大】，揵【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0491011"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">揵</rdg></app>連比丘。南無覺意。名聞邊北方健陀摩
<lb n="0491b08" ed="T"/><note n="0491012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">呵＝訶【三】</note><note n="0491012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">呵【大】，訶【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0491012"><lem wit="【大】">呵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">訶</rdg></app>衍山。彼有<note n="0491013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">虫＝蟲【元】【明】＊</note><note n="0491013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">虫【大】＊，蟲【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0491013"><lem wit="【大】">虫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">蟲</rdg></app><note n="0491014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔王〕－【三】</note><note n="0491014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0491014"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>名<note n="0491015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">差＝羞【三】</note><note n="0491015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">差【大】，羞【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0491015"><lem wit="【大】">差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">羞</rdg></app>吼無。在某牙齒
<lb n="0491b09" ed="T"/>中止。今當遣使者無敢食<note n="0491016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">某＝其【三】</note><note n="0491016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">某【大】，其【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0491016"><lem wit="【大】">某</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">其</rdg></app>牙。及牙根中牙
<lb n="0491b10" ed="T"/>根中牙邊<app type="star" corresp="#0491013"><lem wit="【大】">虫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">蟲</rdg></app>。不即下器中頭破作七分如鳩
<lb n="0491b11" ed="T"/>羅<note n="0491017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">勤＝勒【三】</note><note n="0491017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">勤【大】，勒【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0491017"><lem wit="【大】">勤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">勒</rdg></app>蟮。梵天勸是呪南無佛。令我所呪皆從
<lb n="0491b12" ed="T"/>如願。</p>
